name: Flamingo - Toy Box
description:
An ideal storage solution - it is hard not to be organised when you have a miss lilly toy box in your kids bedroom or living room. These toy boxes or storage baskets hold a surprising amount – fill with toys, books or anything your little heart desires. This flamingo fabric is bang on trend this season and will brighten any room!

Toy boxes hold their shape well when placed on the ground but also fit perfectly in the famous Ikea Expedit shelving unit. 

Due to fact they are soft and squishy they are perfect when your little one is learning to sit and play.  miss lilly toy boxes are made from the most gorgeous fabric prints and so much prettier than plastic tubs! 

Toy boxes are a popular gift for Christenings and Baby Showers with mini storage boxes also available in complementing fabrics.

Dimensions of large toy boxes measure approximately 28cm x 28cm.

Care for your miss lilly toy box:
-	Spot clean
-	Warm iron

Toy Boxes are all hand made so please be aware position of fabric may vary from one item to the next.

name: Hexagon - Dribble Bib
description:
This clever dribble bib is not only super stylish but also highly effective when your little one is teething! Keep those little chests dry and warm. 

Made from a gorgeous cotton print with a soft fleece backing, messy tots (and mums) will love it! 

The design and funky fabric will mean your bub can wear it all day long and still look stylish when teething.

These dribble bibs fit a newborn up to a toddler 2 years of age.

Each bib is hand made and will be cut on a different part of the fabric, it may not look quite the same as the one pictured. 

Hand made by miss lilly herself!
